@startuml state
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam defaultFontSize 13
skinparam dpi 150
skinparam stateBackgroundColor #F0EEF8
skinparam stateBorderColor #3D108A
skinparam stateArrowColor #2E2E38
skinparam stateFontSize 13
skinparam noteBackgroundColor #E8F8F8
skinparam noteBorderColor #27ACAA
skinparam noteFontSize 12

[*] --> Unanswered : **START** — indicator loaded

Unanswered --> Answered : score entered (1 to 5)
Answered --> Answered : score changed

Answered --> EvidenceCapped : score >= 3 and no evidence
EvidenceCapped --> Answered : evidence provided

Unanswered --> Skipped : skipped\n[not regulatory; under 20% cap]
Answered --> Skipped : skipped\n[not regulatory; under 20% cap]
Skipped --> Unanswered : skip undone

note right of EvidenceCapped
  Effective score forced
  to 2 in the aggregation.
  Provide evidence to
  restore the true score.
end note

note right of Skipped
  Score set to null and
  excluded from the denominators.
  Regulatory indicators
  cannot be skipped.
end note

@enduml
